  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Total hip replacement arthroplasty is a surgery having intra- and postoperative substantial
      blood loss. The investigators will investigate the relationship between the various
      hematologic variables and postoperative bleeding volume.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Completed</overall_status>
